WEBVTT

00:02.234 --> 00:03.735
MARTIN: Today,
we're gonna talk about

00:03.735 --> 00:05.362
a medical condition
known as breakthrough pain.

00:05.362 --> 00:07.656
RANDY: We were curious as to
why nobody says OxyContin

00:07.656 --> 00:10.534
in a video designed
to promote OxyContin.

00:10.534 --> 00:12.160
PATIENT #1:
I'm at a loss for words.

00:12.160 --> 00:13.828
It's just changed my life
for the better.

00:13.828 --> 00:15.413
MARKETER #1: We just did
what they wanted.

00:15.413 --> 00:17.415
They said, "Make a PSA,"
so that's what we shot.

00:17.415 --> 00:19.334
BRIDGET: This drug has
only been on the market

00:19.334 --> 00:20.961
for three years,
and there's already been

00:20.961 --> 00:23.755
a spike in overdoses
and crime rates.

00:23.755 --> 00:26.841
‐ Purdue Pharma is doing
my people a great service,

00:26.841 --> 00:29.219
so God bless 'em for it.

00:29.219 --> 00:31.555
What happens if someone has
breakthrough pain

00:31.555 --> 00:33.932
and they're already
at 40 milligrams?

00:33.932 --> 00:36.226
MARTIN: It is time
to double the dose again

00:36.226 --> 00:38.061
as I present to you,

00:38.061 --> 00:39.521
the 80 milligram pill.

00:39.521 --> 00:41.022
[applause]
‐ Whoo!

00:46.486 --> 00:49.489
[crickets chirping]

00:52.784 --> 00:55.787
