in none of that stuff,

03:49.586 --> 03:51.296
even when I was a kid.

03:51.296 --> 03:52.797
‐ Well, then,
as far as that goes,

03:52.797 --> 03:54.466
you got nothing to worry about.

03:54.466 --> 03:56.301
‐ Unless I end up in hell.

03:56.301 --> 03:57.927
‐ [laughs]
Yeah.

03:57.927 --> 04:00.180
