‐ Well, yeah, there's that.

04:04.976 --> 04:07.479
‐ What do I do about 'em?

04:07.479 --> 04:09.606
‐ Forgive 'em.

04:09.606 --> 04:12.358
Love 'em.

04:12.358 --> 04:13.485
Be patient with 'em.

04:13.485 --> 04:15.028
You never know.
They might surprise you.

04:17.614 --> 04:19.199
Go live your life, Bets.

04:21.659 --> 04:23.703
Sometimes you gotta let it go.

04:25.330 --> 04:26.331
