05:53.668 --> 05:56.212
under a relaxed status.

05:56.212 --> 05:58.006
‐ Germany?
RICHARD: Yes.

05:58.006 --> 06:01.259
If we can obtain
a relaxed status,

06:01.259 --> 06:03.261
