without withdrawals.

07:12.288 --> 07:14.999
Now, you make sure
you show that to your doctors.

07:14.999 --> 07:17.961
[chuckles]
This drug is just amazing.

07:17.961 --> 07:20.797
All right, now,
for a little bit of fun news,

07:20.797 --> 07:23.925
management knows how hard
you all have been working.

07:23.925 --> 07:25.468
And, you know, we wanna do
a little something

