basic facts of the drug,

12:22.014 --> 12:23.766
claiming it is
essentially nonaddictive

12:23.766 --> 12:25.101
when it clearly was.

12:25.101 --> 12:26.852
And these participants involved

12:26.852 --> 12:29.563
were deceived
into participating,

12:29.563 --> 12:31.357
being told it was a PSA
for pain relief

12:31.357 --> 12:33.067
instead of an advertisement
for OxyContin,

12:33.067 --> 12:37.154
and many of them are now
addicted or dead from drug use.

12:37.154 --> 12:40.199
So we request access to all
internal marketing materials,

12:40.199 --> 12:41.742
research, and testing data

12:41.742 --> 12:44.203
to determine
if there are other deceptions

12:44.203 --> 12:46.664
as flagrant as the exhibit
currently for the court.

12:46.664 --> 12:49.917
‐ Your Honor,
statements made by counsel

12:49.917 --> 12:52.461
in no way even resemble
the facts.

12:52.461 --> 12:54.588
My client is aware

12:54.588 --> 12:56.007
there have been
addiction issues

12:56.007 --> 12:57.466
in this part of the world,

12:57.466 --> 12:59.719
but blaming Purdue Pharma
for this

12:59.719 --> 13:02.430
is like blaming Budweiser
for a drunk driver.

13:02.430 --> 13:04.432
It is the fault
of the drug abuser

13:04.432 --> 13:06.600
and not of the manufacturer.

13:06.600 --> 13:09.145
