besides OxyContin?

15:16.856 --> 15:18.649
‐ Why 20?
Why not 10?

15:18.649 --> 15:20.860
‐ It's standard
to individualize the dose

15:20.860 --> 15:22.820
for the patient's needs.

15:22.820 --> 15:24.613
‐ I don't want Oxy.

15:24.613 --> 15:26.282
‐ We don't have anything
as effective.

15:26.282 --> 15:27.700
It is completely safe.

15:27.700 --> 15:29.702
‐ Just‐‐just give me
some Tylenol.

15:32.413 --> 15:35.624
‐ I'm gonna go ahead

15:35.624 --> 15:37.918
and have you guys
look at this pamphlet

15:37.918 --> 15:39.503
