15:49.221 --> 15:51.015
Your margins look clean,
but I'll know for sure

15:51.015 --> 15:53.184
once the, uh, pathology
comes back.

15:53.184 --> 15:54.393
‐ Right.

15:54.393 --> 15:56.854
‐ How are you feeling?

15:56.854 --> 15:58.522
‐ Patient's refusing OxyContin.

15:58.522 --> 16:01.859
He only wants Tylenol.

16:01.859 --> 16:04.195
‐ It won't be strong enough.

16:04.195 --> 16:05.488
Pain's the new
fifth vital sign.

16:05.488 --> 16:07.156
It's the top priority
of this hospital.

16:07.156 --> 16:08.324
We manage it.

16:10.367 --> 16:13.370
‐ Do you have
a strong non‐opioid?

16:13.370 --> 16:15.748
‐ We could go with
1,200 milligrams of Motrin.

16:15.748 --> 16:18.042
It'll knock the edge off,
but it doesn't last 12 hours.

16:18.042 --> 16:19.835
‐ Well, neither does OxyContin.

16:19.835 --> 16:22.004
‐ That'll be fine.
He'll do Motrin.

16:22.004 --> 16:28.010
♪ ♪

16:31.639 --> 16:33.474
